snippet.title: WonderSwan Color Longplay - Kidou Senshi Gundam Seed (OLD)
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: NPI

Another Gundam game, with less action and more dialogues. After you beat the game you have a question at the end, however you get the same answer no matter what you chose. I don't know what it's about. Also you get a score attack mode where you can play any of the levels again. -
Disclaimer: Most videos by World of Longplays use SaveStates!
